title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 3 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 3 2021
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 3: De Blasio calls for Cuomo to resign. Psaki says more lockdowns, mandates are on table, dodges on Biden call for Cuomo to be prosecuted if allegations of harassment were true. If you care about freedom, you’ll stand up to these mandates and passports now before it’s too late to go back to pre-covid normalcy. The Olympics. Will New York force the Buckster to get a shot?
